                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Empowering global talent to connect, collaborate, and create extraordinary work together.</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-3">
                        <a href="#" class="group relative w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-indigo-600 hover:to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/50">
                            <i class="fab fa-facebook-f text-slate-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
                        </a>
